msgid "# triton.language.full"
msgstr "# triton.language.full"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.full`返回一个填充了给定形状和数据类型的标量值的张量"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.full` returns a tensor filled with a scalar value of a given shape and data type."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.full(shape, value, dtype, _semantic=None)¶\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                  | 说明                                   |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------- |\n"
"| `shape`           | `tuple of ints`               | 新数组的形状，例如 (8, 16) 或 (8, ) |\n"
"| `value`            | `scalar`               | 用于填充数组的标量值 |\n"
"| `dtype`            | `tl.dtype`               |  新数组的数据类型，例如 tl.float16  |\n"
"| `_semantic`            | `Optional[str]`               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用|\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------- |\n"
"| `shape` | `tuple of ints` | Shape of the new array, e.g., (8, 16) or (8, ) |\n"
"| `value` | `scalar` | Scalar value used to fill the array |\n"
"| `dtype` | `tl.dtype` | Data type of the new array, e.g., tl.float16 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：完成填充之后的tensor\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: the tensor after padding is completed\n"

