#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:30
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:32
msgid "以下示例实现了返回填充了100数值的(XB,YB,ZB)shape的tensor："
msgstr "The following example implements returning a tensor of shape (XB, YB, ZB) filled with the value 100:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/full.md:34
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_f32(output_ptr,XB : tl.constexpr,YB : tl.constexpr,ZB : tl.constexpr):\n"
"    xidx=tl.arange(0,XB)\n"
"    yidx=tl.arange(0,YB)\n"
"    zidx=tl.arange(0,ZB)\n"
"\n"
"    ret = tl.full((XB,YB,ZB),value = 100,dtype = tl.float32)\n"
"\n"
"    oidx=xidx[:,None,None]*YB*ZB+yidx[None,:,None]*ZB+zidx[None,None,:]\n"
"\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr+oidx,ret)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

